    <item>
      <title>共和党强硬派强制投票罢免议长约翰逊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/gop-hardliners-plan-to-force-vote-on-deposing-speaker-johnson</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名共和党强硬派周三宣布，他们将强制投票罢免众议院议长迈克·约翰逊(Mike Johnson)，这场战斗他们几乎肯定会失败，同时会在一个严重分裂的政党中激起意识形态敌意。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/gop-hardliners-plan-to-force-vote-on-deposing-speaker-johnson</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在加沙停火谈判中面临成败时刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/gaza-cease-fire-talks-biden-needs-a-deal-between-israel-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统迫切需要以色列和哈马斯同意停火，这是解决这场震撼该地区并损害他连任机会的冲突的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/gaza-cease-fire-talks-biden-needs-a-deal-between-israel-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚因通货膨胀飙升而增加警察和军队的工资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/nigeria-increases-pay-for-police-military-as-inflation-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚政府同意将包括警察、军事和情报人员在内的公务员工资提高多达 35%，以应对这个西非国家不断上升的通货膨胀和严重的不安全局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/nigeria-increases-pay-for-police-military-as-inflation-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:39:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
